{"types":[{"section":"\n{{fr-noun|f}}\n\n# {{lb|fr|physics}} [[photodetection]]\n#* {{quote-journal|1=fr|year=1989|author=A. Aspect; P. Grangier; G. Roger|title=Dualité onde-particule pour un photon unique|trans-title=Wave–particle duality for a single photon|journal=Journal of Optics|volume=20|issue=3|doi=10.1088/0150-536X/20/3/003|page=122|text=Dans une description classique de la lumière par une onde électromagnétique, l'intensité lumineuse <math>I(t)</math> est divisée en fractions réfléchie et transmise. Les probabilités de '''photodétection''' pendant la porte de comptage numéro <math>n</math> sont proportionnelles à la lumination pendant cette porte<math display=\"block\">L_n = \\int_{t_n}^{t_n + w} I(t)\\mathrm{d}t</math>(on suppose que les diverses probabilités sont petites devant 1).}}","alt":[],"syn":[],"type":"noun","forms":[{"g":"f","n":"s"}],"html":"<p><span class=\"headword-line\"><strong class=\"Latn headword\" lang=\"fr\">photodétection</strong>&nbsp;<span class=\"gender\"><abbr title=\"feminine gender\">f</abbr></span> (<i>plural</i> <b class=\"Latn form-of lang-fr p-form-of\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/photod%C3%A9tections#French\" title=\"photodétections\">photodétections</a></b>)</span>\n</p><ol><li><span class=\"usage-label-sense\"><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content label-content\"><a href=\"/wiki/physics\" title=\"physics\">physics</a></span><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">)</span></span> <a href=\"/wiki/photodetection\" title=\"photodetection\">photodetection</a>\n<ul><li><div class=\"citation-whole\"><span class=\"cited-source\"><span class=\"None\" lang=\"und\"><b>1989</b></span>, A. Aspect, P. Grangier, G. Roger, “Dualité onde-particule pour un photon unique [<span class=\"e-translation\">Wave–particle duality for a single photon</span>]”, in <cite>Journal of Optics</cite>, volume <span class=\"None\" lang=\"und\">20</span>, number 3, <small><span class=\"neverexpand\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1088%2F0150-536X%2F20%2F3%2F003\">→DOI</a></span></small>, page <span class=\"None\" lang=\"und\">122</span>:</span><dl><dd><div class=\"h-quotation\"><span class=\"Latn e-quotation cited-passage\" lang=\"fr\">Dans une description classique de la lumière par une onde électromagnétique, l'intensité lumineuse <span class=\"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\displaystyle I(t)}\">\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mi>I</mi>\n        <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n        <mi>t</mi>\n        <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{\\displaystyle I(t)}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/e2434c9d80c34c95e25cc81ba6700f756a29dac5\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"\" alt=\"{\\displaystyle I(t)}\"></span> est divisée en fractions réfléchie et transmise. Les probabilités de <b>photodétection</b> pendant la porte de comptage numéro <span class=\"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\displaystyle n}\">\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mi>n</mi>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{\\displaystyle n}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/a601995d55609f2d9f5e233e36fbe9ea26011b3b\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"\" alt=\"{\\displaystyle n}\"></span> sont proportionnelles à la lumination pendant cette porte<span class=\"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"\"><math display=\"block\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\displaystyle L_{n}=\\int _{t_{n}}^{t_{n}+w}I(t)\\mathrm {d} t}\">\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <msub>\n          <mi>L</mi>\n          <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n            <mi>n</mi>\n          </mrow>\n        </msub>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <msubsup>\n          <mo>∫<!-- ∫ --></mo>\n          <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n            <msub>\n              <mi>t</mi>\n              <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n                <mi>n</mi>\n              </mrow>\n            </msub>\n          </mrow>\n          <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n            <msub>\n              <mi>t</mi>\n              <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n                <mi>n</mi>\n              </mrow>\n            </msub>\n            <mo>+</mo>\n            <mi>w</mi>\n          </mrow>\n        </msubsup>\n        <mi>I</mi>\n        <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n        <mi>t</mi>\n        <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <mi>t</mi>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{\\displaystyle L_{n}=\\int _{t_{n}}^{t_{n}+w}I(t)\\mathrm {d} t}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/f405a92f54a953303794acdf79cce7d1bf2b483c\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-display mw-invert skin-invert\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"\" alt=\"{\\displaystyle L_{n}=\\int _{t_{n}}^{t_{n}+w}I(t)\\mathrm {d} t}\"></span>(on suppose que les diverses probabilités sont petites devant 1).</span><dl><dd><small>(please <a href=\"/wiki/Wiktionary:Quotations#Adding_translations_to_quotations\" title=\"Wiktionary:Quotations\">add an English translation</a> of this quotation)</small></dd></dl></div></dd></dl></div></li></ul></li></ol>","trans":["photodetection"]}],"title":"photodétection","id":"9573934","audios":[],"ipas":["/fɔ.tɔ.de.tɛk.sjɔ̃/"],"pronunSection":"\n* {{fr-IPA}}\n\n","pronunHtml":"<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Wiktionary:International_Phonetic_Alphabet\" title=\"Wiktionary:International Phonetic Alphabet\">IPA</a><sup>(<a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:French_pronunciation\" title=\"Appendix:French pronunciation\">key</a>)</sup>: <span class=\"IPA\">/fɔ.tɔ.de.tɛk.sjɔ̃/</span></li></ul>"}